#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.105"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.105:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.105:0.2"
msgid "11. Phāsuvihāravagga"
msgstr "11. Living Comfortably"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.105:0.3"
msgid "105. Phāsuvihārasutta"
msgstr "105. Living Comfortably"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.105:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcime, bhikkhave, phāsuvihārā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these five ways of living comfortably."

msgctxt "an5.105:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.105:1.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno mettaṃ kāyakammaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ hoti "
"sabrahmacārīsu āvi ceva raho ca, mettaṃ vacīkammaṃ … mettaṃ manokammaṃ "
"paccupaṭṭhitaṃ hoti sabrahmacārīsu āvi ceva raho ca."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant consistently treats their spiritual companions with "
"kindness by way of body, speech, and mind, both in public and in private."

msgctxt "an5.105:1.4"
msgid ""
"Yāni tāni sīlāni akhaṇḍāni acchiddāni asabalāni akammāsāni bhujissāni "
"viññuppasatthāni aparāmaṭṭhāni samādhisaṃvattanikāni, tathārūpehi sīlehi "
"sīlasāmaññagato viharati sabrahmacārīhi āvi ceva raho ca."
msgstr ""
"They live according to the precepts shared with their spiritual companions, "
"both in public and in private. Those precepts are uncorrupted, unflawed, "
"unblemished, untainted, liberating, praised by sensible people, not "
"mistaken, and leading to immersion."

msgctxt "an5.105:1.5"
msgid ""
"Yāyaṃ diṭṭhi ariyā niyyānikā niyyāti takkarassa sammā dukkhakkhayāya, "
"tathārūpāya diṭṭhiyā diṭṭhisāmaññagato viharati sabrahmacārīhi āvi ceva raho "
"ca."
msgstr ""
"They live according to the view shared with their spiritual companions, both "
"in public and in private. That view is noble and emancipating, and brings "
"one who practices it to the complete ending of suffering."

msgctxt "an5.105:1.6"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca phāsuvihārā”ti."
msgstr "These are the five ways of living comfortably.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.105:1.7"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
